.TH "SVGAELEMENT.HASH" "3JS" "October 21, 2025" "JavaScript" "JavaScript Reference Manual"
.SH NAME
SVGAElement.hash \- SVGAElement: hash property
.SH SYNOPSIS
The \f[B]\f[CB]hash\f[B]\f[R] property of the \f[CR]SVGAElement\f[R]
interface returns a string representing the fragment identifier,
including the leading hash mark (\f[CR]#\f[R]), if any, in the
referenced URL.
.PP
This property can be set, to change the URL\(cqs fragment (ignores
leading \f[CR]#\f[R]).
.SH VALUE
A string.
.SH SEE ALSO
.IP \(bu 2
SVG \f[CR]<a>\f[R] element
